items.name: Ben 10 omniverse style lora
items.description:
ı guest was only a matter of time before ı made anything ben 10 related , was kinda disappointed fact that nobody made omniverse style lora yet so ı tried to make myself. again “tried”

Probably best lora ı made terms of consistency good generation but style accurately lacking in that department not sure going to make more ben 10 related content since ı try to stay away from my ben 10 personality

 

Here is some of recommending for getting better result for this lora

Lower to weight 0.8

Use Euler a as sample

Before generating image, make sure resolution is at least 812x812

ı use alot of textual inversion so recommending using it, check out generation data

This lora confuses a lot about a body type of characters, since ı did not describe character age like they are teenager or a kid? (sorry )So it sometimes generates a kid rather than a teenager best thing you can do avoid the problem. Write positive prompt to “adult” and negative prompt “child”

CFG scale 7-8.5 give more cartoon accurate result and most consistency good images

Well this lora doesn’t  do perfect job to accurately generating characters design, ı’am sure thought some one going to make kai lora eventually because horniness.

 might  upgrade the lora some day..Anyway, good bye

items.name: Reyna | Valorant
items.description:
LoRA trained on Reyna from Valorant

tags: reyna, 1girl, bodysuit, multicolored hair, purple eyes, dark skin, tattoo

anime: YesMix - v1.6 (original), Zenith - v3

2,5D: SXZ Luma - 0.99 VAE, ERA_09 - v1.0, Aniverse - Aniverse V1.1, DarkSun

better hands LoRA: EnvyBetterHands LoCon - beta2

negative embeddings: Fast Negative Embedding (+ FastNegativeV2) - v2

Recommended settings:

  • Make sure you are aware on the usage instructions of LORA

  • VAE: vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned (for realistic models & 2,5D), kl-f8-anime2, blessed2.vae (for anime models)

  • Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras or DPM++ 2M Karras(euler a for img2img upscaling) from time to time im also using DPM++ 2M alt Karras

  • Steps: 20 to 35

  • Clipskip: 2

  • Upscaler : GitHub - pkuliyi2015/multidiffusion-upscaler-for-automatic1111 4x-UltraSharp(for 2,5D & realistic), 4xAnimesharp(for anime)

  • CFG Scale : 5 to 9 (mostly 7)

  • LORA weight for txt2img: 0.5-1 (for the examples i mostly used 0.8 and 1)

  • Denoise strength upscaling: 0.3 to 0.55

If you want to autocomplete the tags & trigger im using, I recommend using Booru style tag autocompletion for AUTOMATIC1111's Stable Diffusion web UI

For full body shots i recommend using: ComfyUI Impact Pack

or the a1111 alternative GitHub - Bing-su/adetailer

items.description:
Hello! Today I present to you my first concept LoRA for orcs breeders as active partners.

Basically I used orcs from warcraft.

NSFW Model

LoRA was trained on Animefull due to best compitability with all anime / 2.5D checkpoint models.

0.7 - 1 is best weight.

Clip skip 2.

Some necessary tokens for better experience:

Orc, 1boy (sometimes you need delete 1boy if you have conflict with another LoRA).
Also "Maghar" but it works not so good as "orc".

You don't need write green skin.

Prompt depends on NSFW scene that you generate.

Extra info! I recommend you next prompt order for NAI-based mixes (you can see it in my preview arts):

  1. (highres, high quality:1.3) ("masterpiece", "8K" and "trending on pixiv" kill some concepts so I don't use. Be carerful if you try some difficult clothes or concepts.

    Also other lighting / shadows / sharpness / fov / colorful if you need effects are here. Sometimes it doesn't work if style of anime or game was baked in LoRA.

  2. Activation word (from lora civitai page, usually character name), what character is doing (with details), char expressions, camera position, background;

  3. Hair details, face details, jewelry, crowns, hats, etc.

  4. Clothes and shoes; Or nude, naked.

  5. Body details (large breasts, cleavage). Genitals if you want generate it.

Also LoRA trained with some NSFW poses. So you can try it with LoRAs or without it.

Advices for better experience:

·         use highres.fix (If you are sure that your prompt is easy for SD); I prefer x4_Fatal_anime_500000_G, animesharp, foolhardy_remacri, siax with 1.5x - 2x upscale.

· use extention after detailer for better faces. It is better than inpaint.

·         use SD Upscale / Ultimate SD Upscale script in img2img;

·         Use inpaint and sketch (or Photopea) for other details;

·         Use Photoshop / Photopea extension.

I will be glad to receive feedback from you and a demonstration of your art with my LoRA!

Other works.

https://tensor.art/u/604375505701151021

items.name: Leonardo da Vinci SDXL 1.0 art style LoRA (Paintings)
items.description:
If you like what I do please consider supporting me on Patreon and contributing your ideas to my future projects!

Leonardo da Vinci art style LoRA for SDXL 1.0. Leonardo da Vinci is one the most famous artists of all time and now you can generate art similar to his style within your own Stable Diffusion workflow. This model was trained on 1024 x 1024 resolution and is able to produce higher details and greater accuracy than if you were to simply type his name into your prompt.

This LoRA was particularly challenging because all of his paintings are hundreds of years old and have degraded significantly over time. I am pleasantly surprised with the outcome of the model however. I decided to not do any kind of restoration on the training images so you will see cracked and chipped paint as well as other types of flaws in the outputs at higher LoRA weights.

I use this at a weight of around 0.8 - 1 but you may have to adjust the weight up or down to 0.6 incrementally by 0.1 depending on the complexity of your prompt. I used clip skip 1 for all of the images you see uploaded to this page. CFG 7 I think works good for this art style.

The main trigger is dvnc and there are no additional tags for this art style. Be creative with your txt2img or use img2img to guide the basic composition and colors.

Have fun playing around with this remarkable tech and if you like it be sure to review and upload all of your amazing works of art!

items.name: 千反田与折木的幸福生活/氷菓 Lora
items.description:
人家郎才女貌,天生一对,轮到你这妖怪来反对?

——周星驰《大话西游》

大家好，我是chosen鲷，这次给大家带来的是千反田与折木的CP lora。

这其实是一种我对于双人CP图的一种新的尝试，众所周知，双人CP图一直是AI绘画领域一个老大难问题，两个人的描述词会互相污染，如果两个人物lora要一起用的话，也经常会造成污染，之前有用tag语句去分开的做法，但是效果依然不佳，还有lantent couple等插件，但是用起来也很麻烦，而且效果也并不好，所以我就采取了一种新的尝试，就是我不分别用两个人物，我直接找一堆现成的CP图，我直接训练一个双人lora，这样两个人的特征都被lora记住了，就可以很简单的出双人图了。

于是抱着这样的想法我开始了尝试，我首先就想到了折木与千反田这一对，因为有个究极冰菓厨画师mery，画了许多张cp图，所以素材库很充足，于是我首先训练了这个模型，从结果来说，确实还不错，虽然存在着一定的肢体崩坏概率，但是两个人的特征都能记住，基本不会互相污染（前提是要用兼容性好的大模型），而且tag也可以写的很简单，就可以出很好的效果，使用起来非常简单。这个模型算是一个抛砖引玉吧，大家可以按照我这个思路，去训练你想要出的cp图，比如新兰啊，柯哀啊之类的。

说回这个lora，因为素材库很丰富，所以啥都能画，什么校服 正装 居家服 便装 泳衣都可以，tag不会写的就看我例图，建议的权重0.8-1.0

推荐的tag

(masterpiece:1.2), best quality,PIXIV,Eru and Houtarou,
这里写你想要画的内容，空着的话就抽卡
<lora:Eru and Houtarou:1>
Negative prompt: EasyNegative, badhandsv5-neg,Subtitles,word,
Steps: 32, Sampler: DPM++ 2M Karras, CFG scale: 7, Seed: 1804965058, Size: 512x768, Model hash: 52b8ebbd5b, Model: chosen-mix bake vae, Denoising strength: 0.5, Clip skip: 2, Hires upscale: 2, Hires upscaler: R-ESRGAN 4x+, Lora hashes: "Eru and Houtarou: 0d1582914056", Version: v1.4.1

大模型推荐我的impasto 、chosen mix，或者用ghost这类兼容性很好的也可以，其他的一些模型可能带来两人元素相互污染的问题，这点请注意。

感谢大家的下载使用，如果喜欢的话欢迎关注我，我的bilibili pixiv ID均为chosen鲷，欢迎大家关注我的频道https://space.bilibili.com/3867754?spm_id_from=333.1007.0.0，https://www.pixiv.net/users/40911695 谢谢。
